      "comment": "LUCKY WINNER (1) has a strong record this track and trip with eight wins and seven placings from 24 starts. In the money last time at this track (19.97) in a Mix 1/2/3, finishing a 5 length second. Looks the one to beat with even luck. GOODBYE MATE (6) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at Richmond over 401m (22.71) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by half a length. Can measure up again. MELLCAT BAD BOY (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.15) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has the ability to give this a shake. ORSON JIMMY (5) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
